commit.message:
SVG import: Fix stroke-linejoin value name

"miter" is the correct value name as per SVG spec:
https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/painting.html#StrokeLinejoinProperty

Tests: Update shapes-line01 expected png for svg import

With fix for #3809 this test failed. New expected png now matches how
other applications (firefox, gwenview, ...) render the input svg.

SVG import: Fix default stroke-linecap

Was "square", now is "butt" as stated as default value in SVG spec:
https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/painting.html#StrokeLinecapProperty
Fixes #3809

More PolySet Refactoring (#5029)

* Manifold constness fixes
* Added utility: PolySet::createEmpty()
* Renamed private members to have underscore suffix
